potato garden.

00:07:11.970 --> 00:07:14.810 align:middle line:90%
There were pipes underneath.

00:07:14.810 --> 00:07:17.310 align:middle line:90%
So that's a long time ago.

00:07:17.310 --> 00:07:20.040 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't realize that
until I was digging here

00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:25.070 align:middle line:84%
and I got a pipe
like these pipes.

00:07:25.070 --> 00:07:29.600 align:middle line:84%
Now this, this is just
one of the pipes that

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:33.950 align:middle line:84%
