little bit earlier,

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:37.685 align:middle line:84%
getting the frost
out of the soil.

00:07:37.685 --> 00:07:44.742 align:middle line:90%


00:07:44.742 --> 00:07:47.450 align:middle line:84%
