working and live in Solheimar

00:07:50.540 --> 00:07:51.800 align:middle line:90%
come together.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:54.720 align:middle line:84%
And we start the day
by holding hands.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:58.620 align:middle line:84%
