>> Then we have this small
community area here where we can

00:09:21.700 --> 00:09:24.490 align:middle line:84%
sit down, talk about
what we're doing,

00:09:24.490 --> 00:09:29.810 align:middle line:84%
have a sing along with
the scouts, light a fire.

00:09:29.810 --> 00:09:37.910 align:middle line:84%
We have this nice fire
pit like this and heat up.

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:39.660 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes we need
some heat in here.

00:09:39.660 --> 00:09:42.400 align:middle line:90%


00:09:42.400 --> 00:09:46.300 align:middle line:10%
Coming together in a garden
is like a healing process.

00:09:46.300 --> 00:09:49.730 align:middle line:10%
It's not all about
growing something.

00:09:49.730 --> 00:09:54.280 align:middle line:10%
It's more about communication
in the garden itself.

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:56.710 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about
something or having

00:09:56.710 --> 00:10:01.674 align:middle line:84%
a small campfire in the garden,
it's so healing and relaxing.

