00:10:42.890 --> 00:10:45.270 align:middle line:90%
for apple trees in the country.

00:10:45.270 --> 00:10:50.070 align:middle line:84%
So we're going to put all
the types of apple trees,

00:10:50.070 --> 00:10:53.690 align:middle line:90%
and there are lots in Solheimar.

00:10:53.690 --> 00:10:55.490 align:middle line:84%
So they can come every
