And they bring the trees,
but we to get the fruits

00:11:03.245 --> 00:11:04.045 align:middle line:90%
when they come.

00:11:04.045 --> 00:11:09.480 align:middle line:90%


00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:15.030 align:middle line:84%
Everything we do here belongs
to the people in Solheimar.

00:11:15.030 --> 00:11:16.300 align:middle line:90%
We don't sell anything.

00:11:16.300 --> 00:11:18.990 align:middle line:84%
