We have a lot of
areas in Solheimar.

00:11:46.750 --> 00:11:50.430 align:middle line:90%
We still have to put trees down.

00:11:50.430 --> 00:11:53.370 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, there's so
many possibilities.

00:11:53.370 --> 00:11:55.500 align:middle line:84%
And in Solheimar,
all the villages

00:11:55.500 --> 00:12:00.280 align:middle line:84%
