00:12:06.390 --> 00:12:08.680 align:middle line:90%
taking salads for the dinner.

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:11.080 align:middle line:84%
So everybody who
lives in Solheimar

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:14.270 align:middle line:90%
have a free use of the garden.

00:12:14.270 --> 00:12:15.560 align:middle line:90%
They can weed.

00:12:15.560 --> 00:12:18.520 align:middle line:84%
They can take salads
whenever they want.

00:12:18.520 --> 00:12:21.310 align:middle line:84%
It's open for everybody
who lives in Solheimar

00:12:21.310 --> 00:12:25.000 align:middle line:90%
to use the garden as they want.

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:26.630 align:middle line:84%
If you're doing the
permaculture way,

00:12:26.630 --> 00:12:32.080 align:middle line:84%
you have to realize that
things don't happen tomorrow.

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:33.650 align:middle line:90%
You have to take your time.

00:12:33.650 --> 00:12:36.436 align:middle line:90%
It takes a while.

00:12:36.436 --> 00:12:40.010 align:middle line:84%
First year, maybe you
look at your site.

00:12:40.010 --> 00:12:42.190 align:middle line:84%
Where is the sun and
how is the water going?

00:12:42.190 --> 00:12:46.070 align:middle line:84%
And how is the soil, and
are there trees there?

00:12:46.070 --> 00:12:50.920 align:middle line:84%
How can you use these
trees to make growth?

00:12:50.920 --> 00:12:55.090 align:middle line:84%
And then the next year, you have
a little bit idea about what

00:12:55.090 --> 00:12:56.360 align:middle line:90%
happened the year before.

00:12:56.360 --> 00:12:58.930 align:middle line:84%
Then you can start
slowly but surely.

00:12:58.930 --> 00:13:00.970 align:middle line:90%
And things take time.

